Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the principal could go to heaven thanks to you.{Thanks to you, the principal managed to go to heaven.（優作）\N君のおかげで　園長先生は→\N\N天国に行けたようだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?{（亮佑）ホント？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time you leave someone an offering though, you should talk about it with your parents first.{However, from now on you should talk with your parents before [you give / giving] any offerings.でも　今度お供えする時は→} {ご両親に\N相談してからにするといい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it!{うん！わかった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, keep what happened today a secret to everybody.{You should also keep this a secret from everyone.それと　今回のことは\N誰にも内緒だよ。}
