Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...he probably said something fitting just like that...{I think he probably said something appropriate like that...とかなんとか　適当なこと\N言ってたんじゃないかなぁ...。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm relieved to know that Dad didn't run off on that case...{Well, unlike what I [had] thought, dad hadn't backed off from that case.\N[I'm relieved / What a relief]... / まぁ　俺的には→\N父さんが事件をバックレたわけじゃないとわかって→\N\Nホッとしたって...。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...{コ...　コナン君...。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...right?{だよね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, I was just reading from Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}'s e-mail...{Right now I was [just] reading what Shin'ichi-niichan had written in his mail... / あっ　今のは　新一兄ちゃんのメールを読んだだけで...。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, don't scare me like that!{Sheesh, don't startle me like that!もぉ～！\Nビックリさせないでよ～！}
