Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...{ご　ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shame.{Still... what a shame, right?でも　残念よね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the case is finally solved,{Even we solved this case we were highly anticipating,せっかく\N今回の事件　解けたのに→} we still don't know who the thief was...{we don't know who the thief was...窃盗犯が\Nわからないなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:20:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this bloody ¥10 coin I found under the vending machine could be a clue.{[Perhaps] this 10-yen coin with blood I found underneath the vending machine could be a clue.手がかりなら\Nこの自販機の下から→} {血の付いた\N１０円玉を見つけたよ。}
