Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, y-yeah...{えっ？あっ　う　うん...。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not going to the police station?{Huh? you won't come with us to the police? / え？世良さん\N警察に行かないの？}
